{"tid":611384,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好懷念IQ雙拼?","createTime":"2018-03-31T03:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T15:57:38.000Z","uid":70197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2026b5c331bb29ed9fa66da928bf18f454e362a7","tid":611384,"uid":70197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:19:50.000Z","msg":"仲記得小一個陣咁啱遇到SARS，响屋企無所事事自然會睇電視。<br />\n雖然屋企冇有線電視，但唔知點解有免費有線電視第一台所以可以睇IQ非典型。之後就變咗做IQ雙拼。<br />\n個陣真係會好傻係咁打電話希望可以抽中自己直播玩遊戲。<br />\n點知真係中咗，仲要同我同學一齊玩勁搞笑。<br />\n仲要特登老點咗我呀媽去荃灣拎獎品同Amen呀bean親筆簽名。<br />\n好記得呀bean成個洋蔥頭咁，Amen就係戴眼鏡好瘦嘅。<br />\n佢兩個仲要出咗本IQ題書。<br />\n見到宜家啲小朋友好似無哂童年回憶咁好慘，一放學就要補呢樣返唔同興趣班。<br />\n自己真係好幸福!<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/111937_59dada7abf2653f07c792ccfef94cde5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F111937_59dada7abf2653f07c792ccfef94cde5.jpg&h=3d733237&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69a2455a712ffd29d540b2d4a9e4b75b28e67654","tid":611384,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"最估唔到Amen竟然走左去拍鴨王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb8c2326478c5d6729d630858eb9df052409f61","tid":611384,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:57:38.000Z","msg":"bean哥哥有啲似simon pegg"}]}